{"arkId":"cl010103367","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010103367","modified ":"2025-10-04","title":"Buste du duc de Berry","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Buste du duc de Berry"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1822","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 559 - Louis XVIII, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 559, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1822,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Rutxhiel, Henri Joseph","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1775","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1837","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3130412"},{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"},{"label":"Brachard, Alexandre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribuable \u00e0","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"R\u00e9gnier, Hyacinthe","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribuable \u00e0","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11791","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"buste","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Buste en biscuit de Charles-Ferdinand d\u0027Artois, duc de Berry, en costume militaire portant les insignes royaux, la plaque et le grand cordon de l\u0027ordre du Saint-Esprit, la croix de la L\u00e9gion d\u0027honneur et la croix de l\u0027ordre de Saint-Louis. \r\n\r\nMarques en creux : M(s). 29 n\u00b01; Mf ; sous le pied : 25-12 ; 2.\r\n\r\nD\u00e8s 1814, le directeur de la manufacture de S\u00e8vres, Alexandre Brongniart, fait r\u00e9aliser un moulage du buste du duc de Berry model\u00e9 par le sculpteur Ruxthiel ; ce pl\u00e2tre est toujours conserv\u00e9 \u00e0 la manufacture de S\u00e8vres. La manufacture en \u00e9dite \u00e0 partir de 1816 des r\u00e9ductions. Apr\u00e8s l\u0027assassinat du prince en f\u00e9vrier 1820, Brongniart d\u00e9cide de faire ex\u00e9cuter le buste, \u0022aussi grand que nature\u0022. Deux exemplaires sont ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s, l\u0027un par Alexandre Brachard, l\u0027autre par Hyacinthe R\u00e9gnier. La non visibilit\u00e9 des marques ne permet pas de pr\u00e9ciser de quel exemplaire il s\u0027agit.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0,758","displayDimension":"0,758 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,63","displayDimension":"0,63 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,38","displayDimension":"0,38 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : c\u00e9ramique\r\nMat\u00e9riau : biscuit de porcelaine dure","placeOfCreation":"S\u00e8vres (Ile-de-France = Ile de France-\u003EHauts-de-Seine = Hauts de Seine)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Offert par Louis XVIII \u00e0 la duchesse de Berry ; ch\u00e2teau de Frohsdorf, acquisition en 1995","jabachInventory":"","n